column3: the food is quite tasty in a diabetes-inducing kind of way in reference to pancakes and other sugar-laden treats.   The ambience
column4: and I guess some diners like it
column5: made us extremely uncomfortable. The music is super loud and jarring and not in sync with chill morning vibes.  Parking is a major hassle at this location.  But if u like blaring music and sugary treats
